  "keyFeatures": [
    "Physics-based ships and moving structures in Minecraft",
    "Ship assembly and disassembly API for mod developers",
    "Buoyancy simulation with air pocket support",
    "Multi-loader support (Fabric, Quilt, Forge)",
    "Block mass/friction/elasticity data pack system",
    "Mod compatibility with Create, ComputerCraft, Dynmap, Hex Casting, and more",
    "BlockEntityPhysicsListener for physics-thread block entity callbacks",
    "Coordinate space utilities for ship-world transformations"
